{"hec2b4e7ag57b2g44a5gb23bg8ab64eacf882": ["It's not the same here. Feels emptier.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "714d0570-ce3e-5b03-3090-45b249616877"], "h7f99a258g22c4g41a8gb9e9g39049f87ef88": ["What's wrong?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "5097465f-6575-6b1c-a8ba-d47a028d8ac1"], "hec747084g7dbdg4acdgbc28g59e54cac995b": ["The young cub. He's gone... for good.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "4d815c00-faff-75e6-18c4-34e3c2564b2d"], "h77970f72g404ag4ac1gbb0ega7199c2f3855": ["*The dog looks up at you, his eyes big and mournful.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "84fb1ce3-edbd-93b5-09e0-2b304ca15819"], "ha406746egc190g41cbga2bcgd5b28e8aa162": ["<i>Pet the dog.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1ddd5321-4454-e657-eb4c-58904b02f741"], "h520cb1d2g2994g4ab1ga61agdafe467a37bd": ["Thank you. I needed that.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "70312fde-a116-9b8e-a87f-27a16edfe3ed"], "hd6ee7920g48d4g4d00gb00eg0f2e53c36028": ["*The dog gives a soft whine of appreciation.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "a80bc8ec-6575-5c3b-4b4f-34623590115c"], "hd69bb8e1gd4dbg4ad2gab7fg85f09fb3f273": ["<i>Pet the dog.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "87f58730-63a5-1303-90bf-dc9736c20ed4"], "h0326e13bg2851g4e27g8a6ega6d28f7b5fe6": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "59c6f312-5b26-588b-031c-4de15acdde66"], "hb40a3a3bg5d46g4ecfg895eg6d6e54ca99d1": ["*Whine.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "31063621-6b0a-555e-2f06-7181231bf3e2"], "hefa8e07fgae27g49f0gab77g10896bb91021": ["Hope you're keeping well, friend.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "852c15a1-7b8c-412f-495b-916c9ad508a5"], "he3fc82afg4640g4338gb4d3g9a503067955d": ["*The dog holds a well-chewed ball in his mouth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "071a4d90-ee55-4968-3bce-a8ca1e3a317f"], "h82d40c31g9c58g44b0g947cg310a5cfc4704": ["Hand that over.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "a12c7b10-91a2-c22a-5906-469b6029020d"], "he8cee65cgdebbg40d8g9e2cg7e44af2aaa5c": ["All right. It's only fair that you enjoy it, too.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "dc7802ef-08d6-139c-0713-a16d65711e82"], "h2ebfb259ga1eag4dedg9698gc2341d2ce446": ["But if you feel like throwing it - I wouldn't mind that at all.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "8255ee6e-dcf3-26a4-3c47-219b94edddee"], "hd9c2ad3bg4c76g49fcgadacg220e826453e2": ["I didn't introduce myself before. You can call me Scratch.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "590b01c2-e7ff-f4f0-206a-2b3b3a3c04ac"], "hc687dd3cgfa24g401ega4e0g23b694567515": ["<i>Look him over for any signs of injury from the owlbear cub.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "f55a1d48-6e72-9e3c-6820-4aafa1412ba0"], "h86d639fdg945dg4158gb9dfg6c5c298e949d": ["*Nothing - he's fine. It seems the cub didn't attack Scratch, despite the sounds you heard in the night.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "8ee87310-0da0-6368-83db-727b0c5ecf82"], "h0835e999gf7d6g44b8gbbecgf8a37ec24e4c": ["I heard you and the owlbear cub in the night - I thought something might've happened to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3116b92c-1115-d3ef-36b4-8d0248b431e8"], "hc24a1b82g02d4g499bg996eg2734700ef474": ["No, nothing happened - just the young one having bad dreams. That's what you heard.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "da19ba2f-89b2-d416-8c2b-d1dc49ccb987"], "hf52d97fdgffe9g4574gbbb4g1edc8a63554d": ["I stay with him and keep him company when he's scared. He'll settle down, in time.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "663d52a8-9ded-6ce6-17b8-c44f4a932841"], "h94458b48ge34ag425fg9a44g236b09ccdf00": ["I hear you're friends with the owlbear cub.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "16f564ca-6b29-d843-e0c9-5c0b777071bb"], "h80e47aaag8193g47adga26cgdfed6587c587": ["Yes! He's a handful, but I like having him around.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "014cd8fd-9089-ceb3-bcf5-03da4c7ccb84"], "hf7a91201g6c0dg404ag8206gdbd0af3473e5": ["I'm sorry, about what happened to your master.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d93cfcef-a730-7fd6-80cf-084e27027116"], "h499a628fg553fg432dg846fg769c9251af30": ["Master, friend... I stayed with him until... until I knew he was gone.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d74427fa-ac81-8c0d-94ac-a8a41a251809"], "h6e879a4fgdadeg4af8gb40ag517b5749843c": ["I'll never forget him, but I'm glad to have met you.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1e21576c-d7b7-df71-08a2-bddf4067e13a"], "h96899328g7f0ag4907ga21dg85cc74351088": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "81d709f0-42d4-f854-77cf-e24170f22985"], "h25a90a18gd134g4affga154g4a083c7dc90f": ["Oh - thank you. That's... that's nice.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "6f033f86-62e2-e94a-c845-1df1b3cd6a0b"], "hb9c29e3eg3e35g497bg9312g2ffb24e83ecb": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "9f33e02e-c647-76db-eaae-c40c3c25e1ed"], "h79fded3fgfffag485bgbf94g6624e9c80e79": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3c0b8c48-4d39-ed90-41d5-2623b8557e3e"], "hc3f606a8ga300g453aga734g6bdbb04a528e": ["<i>Let him keep it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "13cc5137-216a-1a8c-85ae-b6eea530cb37"], "h853e66a4g739cg49aegb575gcda310b79959": ["*The dog holds what appears to be a bloodied rodent in his jaws.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "e1895b93-7567-2600-e54b-18d62dc010be"], "h614e14c9g41f7g4c2bg8bf9g3da2d589cefa": ["_", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "9c767846-fa31-8fc1-67b4-c176a2c39b44"], "h5462dbf7g7f64g47cbgaae1g97a31b1fe58e": ["Let go of that - carefully.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "057dabf8-5e69-7151-03f3-567aa98babbb"], "h40557cc8g601eg4125ga550gee80c0bae131": ["There. Carefully, like you said.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3436020d-69ef-2ae6-95e5-6388a2e9a736"], "hae6461d9g7d85g47b3g8c31g09034a6987c3": ["Hm. They're no fun after they stop running.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3033934a-c922-91b2-bf19-50080c8c8e4f"], "h25eafca9g6b8eg4f15ga80dgacd3eb60b1c0": ["Drop that - <i>right now.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "8fd3b860-3228-9f70-4deb-72e1b52507ee"], "hc7c89dd3gb181g45fbga47ag383a854116f4": ["Fine. There's no need to yell.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "eb0488ea-bd52-d0a6-25ee-f97ab9f4c274"], "h0e0be206g8ae6g4491g9469g4f3342fbc5f0": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1c58890b-cd50-d9ef-cc0c-b82452d7e453"], "hc2d65551g5434g48c4gaf7eg29f63212d91d": ["_", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1ef57070-25ae-86a6-0049-c7ffdb1da51d"], "hca671facg0c5bg47aegb475g6aaaee9a656d": ["<i>Let him keep it.</i>", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "b2a49fdc-a999-4e2d-1ea3-38b4b308971c"], "hbb090b4fg8631g4bedg9668g8fa451bc4ef5": ["*The dog holds what appears to be a bloodied rodent in his jaws.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "ac9e316d-925a-f8a6-2424-429659b63f3e"], "h30a3dea2g25ddg42fbg8fa5g480981ac3a6c": ["*The dog is unable to speak through the small bag he holds in his mouth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "99c69eae-01fe-c119-f3a6-0ff127f8fdbd"], "h092e0b30gf50eg4f88g91aagc77d135d68d7": ["What've you got there, Scratch?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "fad1d266-ce22-de4e-f2e5-c379193b0cf1"], "h5af375aag0266g4a38gbfc7gf1a4ef5f132b": ["I don't know. Maybe you can tell me. ([CAMP_Courier_Dog_FetchedItemDescription_50004d01-651b-a7ea-308a-451a9571cb85])", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "29ae3b38-eaad-10dc-c243-8485aa6b6c16"], "hef2fcc15g1a80g4f5eg8914gbccc630336bf": ["All I know is I thought of you when I saw it.", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "78559e42-901e-4c7f-e606-adbbe0aa160d"], "h9665c766ga040g4158g861bg3a8f1b75f28f": ["Hand that over.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1981be9d-884f-769e-195d-b331acb06d0b"], "h6b949f4ag6b23g4245g89aag9f07a1e44872": ["Here. I hope you like it. ([CAMP_Courier_Dog_FetchedItemDescription_50004d01-651b-a7ea-308a-451a9571cb85])", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3ae08ee5-1c1b-4903-bb22-dd5f998f39c1"], "hb3e41a5dg9e09g4e38gbd7eg1af7e284b1d7": ["<i>Let him keep it.</i>", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "c31667b9-f832-dc2e-8dbd-48b11e66218a"], "h7719b4a4gd797g40a9ga40agbc85f3c7900e": ["*Scratch's tail wags enthusiastically.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "453979b3-148c-caee-f58d-b668cd0ca223"], "hd59da339g91b2g4101gab09g1109c415f486": ["<i>Look him over for any signs of injury from the owlbear cub.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "ac01875c-1624-3c1f-b497-49a15e5173a2"], "hfc731f9bg80bag4973g8d45ge35b20452b90": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1b7a401f-8b7e-d9bc-a40a-b99bf24a4738"], "h5d87ce3dg9dcag4717gbfc5g5760f55d540e": ["<i>Pet him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "e9f54df2-010f-50e0-11a7-597d9f22637b"], "h71bbd894gf1a6g493fg93a0g1c926c90df58": ["*Scratch's tongue lolls out happily, his tail wagging even faster.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d25ec3be-232b-ba78-ee74-5f3f167a488b"], "he08568cagbea4g4958gab1fgf61e7f18c195": ["*Pant.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "509511ef-c653-5c05-effc-b9746c6f6ee8"], "ha956a3c8g6ddeg42ecg83b6g04910edfbf33": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "91a93c68-45fb-3c78-543e-9b3cf04b93af"], "hb0feae49gda28g42a6gbc89gfc20fd8e3940": ["*Bark!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "8f7be959-9cda-0ec5-2aa7-5ecdff8b8ef7"], "ha10410fcgfdd1g4035ga2dag65db3d09af92": ["*You spot a name on the dog's collar - 'Scratch'.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "5388e096-f538-a289-4840-fa711ed9c66a"], "hf12c8310g7867g450cg9769g214675f19e8f": ["*The dog pants through a ball held firmly in his mouth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "5b250284-3d9c-973c-c964-aebf09cc5761"], "hf4236c80gc73eg49b8gb381g110c1fa00471": ["Hand it over, boy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "43a4c646-6829-3481-61f5-bd56e26c0c8b"], "h596db675ga3f3g42e5gb224g33aeebd5631f": ["*He relinquishes the ball. It is well-chewed and slick with drool.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "93107bb7-4216-4879-bf7a-54b9695f005f"], "h76449394gb6a2g4c15g9734gee5ca726c8ec": ["*His eyes track the ball avidly. He shuffles on his paws, ready to chase after it...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "edd327da-f060-d668-1239-2f68e3ccdf9c"], "hf0ca1adag3722g4b49gb545g85bc1721795b": ["*Arf! Arf!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "7b8821a4-0f08-e562-6557-c2643437528e"], "hc6de3b3ag6001g4ae5g9ba3gba3410a0db87": ["<i>Wrestle the ball from him.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d2653dfa-de28-b783-4747-a8c9a02935c4"], "h4c13dd56g2c66g472cga59eg8a2be139cc66": ["*Grrrr.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "888127c4-19e5-99ed-85ed-6936b7679399"], "h42f49456g1477g49f4gb6afg0151a3ae7ac9": ["<i>Distract him with one hand and slip the ball from his jaws with the other.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "761b1d44-addd-2ad7-37f4-9e37a55a2415"], "h672507d0g7296g4a3fg8971g0e984581ff86": ["<i>Encourage him to drop the ball.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d8f59d57-9635-095c-6dfc-bd0207bda0ad"], "h264b6d1cg8f87g4cf9ga02ag3d78004038c0": ["<i>Let him keep the ball.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "063a9108-ca3b-8d93-e4c1-2fcde0575529"], "h2afdbe9bgfd9cg4d0dgaf6eg0783c1e61708": ["*You spot a small bundle of bloodied fur nestled between the dog's teeth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d9f32afb-ca35-3654-8011-17a1a33a0a34"], "h8e499080g3ef7g4418g90abg1fd3e212d4f5": ["Give that here. It's not for eating.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "d2fdc030-d722-1bba-1a0e-1a01e45380c6"], "h3d0afcc0g7b1ag437agbf52g593fdec83ac4": ["<i>Lean in for a closer look.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "ea311a0f-13b6-9a3f-8861-0690d9126bfb"], "h98c10987g16f4g46e1g9f94g9c090f0e41da": ["*It is impossible to identify the creature while it's in his mouth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "1a7d5930-355d-7dc7-10dd-f72116857786"], "hcb340952gc557g416bg948bg3dd1114e9961": ["Give that here. It's not for eating.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "89651989-11ea-936c-b48a-b1ed84d91c50"], "h9916b055g20b3g40b3g9b87g0a6b8f244c0b": ["_", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "52c8772c-e563-84ce-2b88-2a1a01b9dedd"], "h3cc24690g8753g49a0g8f66g22f9f35936b7": ["*The dog gives a happy bark, clearly proud of his hunting skills.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "eb7a78e6-658c-ff27-b1d7-dcfe9cc7ad80"], "h9f4312efg0a5cg477bga982g805c48d22bd6": ["*Arf! Arf!*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "548e5f46-9fae-31cc-3a86-db4f301b69f8"], "h4081bca4g133bg4fdagb7e6gce7f96eca3e9": ["*Scratch digs in his paws and clamps his teeth down defiantly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "ba24950c-8a4a-f371-4a35-dccffdff83ee"], "h94ba6515gda08g4b35gba3dg671345f9293c": ["Drop that, now!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "61c82a9c-62dc-f76f-98f5-2c1e8dfc4905"], "hd3a49429g6cceg468cgb24agc1c02bc534aa": ["_", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "3120dadb-437f-6024-68ed-8fe76cf8eaf1"], "h79209ac1gb982g438fga18bg6e2b74ffbd24": ["<i>Pry the furry shape from his mouth.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "111cf40b-6bea-3b8c-1a4b-504f4623f663"], "h6bbbce5fgce48g4846gbb14g0acf670d9e96": ["<i>Let him keep the creature.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "c5c85b2f-4d9a-e26a-9599-fac4e31d13a7"], "h75d8600fg020bg4f1egb94fgb030a52ae9ba": ["*You spot a small bundle of bloodied fur nestled between the dog's teeth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "2a9bf9fe-ac8e-a6a1-027b-af5d6cdff5c4"], "h8859b3b1g0d30g49b5g937fg6173feee56b4": ["*The dog wags his tail, a small bag clenched between his teeth.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "e0c6ec5d-c7b0-83ff-aa09-ebc3b8a25398"], "h90c5764eg5ad6g48c2g934eg13b00207eec1": ["Give that here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "00179e95-8da8-2e90-553b-7648e4580ec5"], "h42a7dd56g7d99g4b28gb812g4b176ab5c5c7": ["*He gives in and surrenders his find to you.* ([CAMP_Courier_Dog_FetchedItemDescription_50004d01-651b-a7ea-308a-451a9571cb85])", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "89c67f46-57c5-386e-2778-3b928e566e75"], "h36e13e18g79e5g425ega0d8g3b65ab06fc8b": ["<i>Reach forward and yank at it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "f78086ac-aec3-7f8f-9e91-39674a4e4fdb"], "h460cd9degb281g4033g821fgcb7c1e52ecb7": ["*Grrr.*", "3059f69c-068d-4e28-8491-55953c027901", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "4b403bc0-03b3-fcec-dee1-be81dc52cc57"], "h66814076gf632g40fbg82fdgcbb5a44dbc7b": ["<i>Snatch it away quickly.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\CAMP_Courier_Dog.html", "c23ea086-20ca-0b6d-ddea-c4c35a8ae54a"], "hf3fabc75gb7d0g4409g936ag60df1481d9b0": ["<i>Extend a palm and wait expectantly.</i>", "e0